* Used for receiving GPS satellite measurements from the GPS engine.
     * Each measurement contains raw and computed data identifying a satellite.
     * You can implement this interface and call {@link LocationManager#addGpsMeasurementListener}.
     *
     * @hide

methods.name: void onGpsMeasurementsReceived(GpsMeasurementsEvent eventArgs)
methods.comment: * Returns the latest collected GPS Measurements.

methods.name: void onStatusChanged(int status)
methods.comment: * Returns the latest status of the GPS Measurements sub-system.
